OL,3,CFather of Southport killer tells
OL,4,Cinquiry he was frightened of violent
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FThe teenager murdered Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, seven, Bebe King, six, and
OL,9,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, in his
OL,10,Fattack on a Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,11,Fclass on 29 July 2024.
OL,13,FIn a statement, he said the
OL,14,Fcombination of fear and "the desire to
OL,15,Favoid confrontation" prevented him
OL,16,Ffrom doing things expected of a
OL,17,Fparent, such as monitoring his
OL,18,Finternet activities or inquiring about
OL,19,Fitems he ordered online.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@TO]
