OL,3,CFather of Southport killer tells
OL,4,Cinquiry he was frightened of violent
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FHe added: "This had catastrophic
OL,8,Fconsequences for which I am
OL,9,Fdesperately sorry."
OL,11,FHe went on to say: "I accept that I
OL,12,Fbear my share of the responsibility
OL,13,Fand that by not challenging AR's
OL,14,Fbehaviour he was allowed to acquire
OL,15,Fdangerous weapons and view
OL,16,Finappropriate content online."
OL,18,FNicholas Moss KC, counsel to the
OL,19,Finquiry, asked if he accepted he
OL,20,Fshould have exercised more
OL,21,Fresponsibility over AR.
OL,26,@oD@KOUqD@SO]sD@TOUxD@^O]
