OL,3,CFather of Southport killer tells
OL,4,Cinquiry he was frightened of violent
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FAlphonse R said: "I tried before and
OL,8,Fhe was violent."
OL,10,FHe told the inquiry of an incident in
OL,11,Fearly 2024 when his son "poured a
OL,12,Fsignificant quantity of oil" over his
OL,13,Fhead and threatened to kill him.
OL,15,FHe said: "His eyes were very red and
OL,16,Fit seemed he had some kind of mental
OL,17,Fanguish, some kind of mental pain."
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@PO]sD@YOUtD@\O]wD@JOUyD@cO]
