OL,3,CFather of Southport killer tells
OL,4,Cinquiry he was frightened of violent
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FAlphonse R said that his son poked his
OL,8,Fchest and said "if you get me out of
OL,9,Fhere, this house, it may take a day, a
OL,10,Fweek, or it may be years, I will kill
OL,11,Fyou and trust me I will kill you".
OL,13,F"He looked seriously at me and it was
OL,14,Fquite frightening actually," he said.
OL,16,FThe inquiry heard AR was permanently
OL,17,Fexcluded from Range High School in
OL,18,FOctober 2019 after he admitted in a
OL,19,Fcall to Childline that he had taken a
OL,20,Fknife to school on 10 occasions.
