OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FAlphonse R denied that and said they
OL,8,Fwere "dying inside" because of what
OL,9,Fhad happened.
OL,11,F"We sent a beautiful boy who was
OL,12,Fcapable, who was very well dressed,
OL,13,Fwho looked after himself, to Range
OL,14,FHigh," he said.
OL,16,F"By the time they sent him back to us
OL,17,Fhe was broken, disappointed,
OL,18,Ftraumatised, changed completely beyond
OL,19,Fbelief so now we are dealing with a
OL,20,Fdifferent AR at Acorns."
