OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FHe said: "Nobody knew at home."
OL,9,FAlphonse R, who was born in Rwanda and
OL,10,Fmoved to the UK in 2002, was seen
OL,11,Fduring his evidence only by the
OL,12,Finquiry team, with members of the
OL,13,Fpublic, press and other participants
OL,14,Fhearing an audio feed.
OL,16,FThe inquiry was adjourned until
OL,17,FThursday, when he and his wife
OL,18,FLaetitia Muzayire will give evidence.
